*** Release glite-data-transfer-cli_R_3_7_0_1 2009-07-03

	o v3.7.0 of the interface with checksum support.

	  glite-transfer-submit can take the -K option for checksum comparison
	  and can pass on optional checksums (algorithm:hexadecimal-numbers)
	  for each source-destination SURL pair given by the command line or
	  in a job description file.

